Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim YLHL As String Dim UAS_1 As String Dim UAS_2 As String Dim UAM As String
YLHL = Text_YLHL.Caption UAS_1 = Text_UAS_1.Caption UAS_2 = Text_UAS_2.Caption UAM = Text_UAM.Caption
FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = "SourceName LIKE '%" & YLHL & "%' or SourceName LIKE '%" & UAS_1 & "%' or SourceName LIKE '%" & UAS_2 & "%' or SourceName LIKE '%" & UAM & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub

Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
